{"tid":1476040,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[KPOP] PRODUCE_X101所有練習生及X1討論區 (102) 香港加油！X1出道仲有14日咋！","createTime":"2019-08-15T16:16:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T16:23:23.000Z","uid":87211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"46346d763fdc7c48b68dbff981d6c98888d52afa","tid":1476040,"uid":87211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:16:42.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>歡迎各位連登製作人<br />\n你可以係度發表有關PRODUCE X 101所有練習生及組合X1既意見<br />\n最重要互相尊重 一齊維持良好和諧既氣氛</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>X1<br />\n엑스원</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/msQYuVj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmsQYuVj.png&h=e0146c6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EAFayYTUcAAMayL?format=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEAFayYTUcAAMayL%3Fformat%3Djpg&h=6fa1219e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LZqHWGh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLZqHWGh.png&h=41ebf68d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D_wDEoTU8AAT592?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FD_wDEoTU8AAT592%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dlarge&h=153bf647&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">X1（韓語：엑스원 X Won）是由Mnet選秀節目《PRODUCE X 101》的出道承諾，由最終決選出線的11名成員所組成，於2019年成立的韓國男子音樂組合，成員名單以投票方式決定。<br />\n成員依排名為金曜漢、金宇碩、韓勝宇、宋亨俊、曹承衍、孫東杓、李翰潔、南道賢、車俊昊、姜敏熙、李垠尚。<br />\n2019年整體以SWING娛樂旗下藝人身份出道（各自則有所屬的經紀公司），進行為期5年的限定活動，前2.5年為專屬合約，後2.5年可於原本公司進行活動。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">要安俊英年早逝？<br />\n唔洗用劍嘅！<br />\n用李鎭赫旋風夠晒威<br />\n赫旋風的確好洗！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9qxZZe8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9qxZZe8.gif&h=0833c36d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCr to 藍色女人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>正名更好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong>之參賽者花名表</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/u/1/d/1urtD3aMQ76E5zpYMJAjGKMJEmGWJZAGw_v_VXOlMZ6w/htmlview\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fu%2F1%2Fd%2F1urtD3aMQ76E5zpYMJAjGKMJEmGWJZAGw_v_VXOlMZ6w%2Fhtmlview&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPEgDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=76afa987\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/u/1/d/1urtD3aMQ76E5zpYMJAjGKMJEmGWJZAGw_v_VXOlMZ6w/htmlview</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K0EtSc2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK0EtSc2.gif&h=238a2118&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"479aa1030cd80ae23b256760ee04be2bb6a25065","tid":1476040,"uid":261782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:18:15.000Z","msg":"牙熙lm<br />\n<img src=\"https://t1.daumcdn.net/cfile/tistory/99F089355D55790511\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft1.daumcdn.net%2Fcfile%2Ftistory%2F99F089355D55790511&h=540ceca1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1WJ3ytT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1WJ3ytT.jpg&h=0a3d9308&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sZPybfy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsZPybfy.jpg&h=0005e3b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mmhvXVz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmmhvXVz.jpg&h=899400d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GEoV82e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.